"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-news-2024-8-11-algerias-imane-khelif-files-harassment-case-after-gender\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympic boxing champion's lawyer condemns 'speculations fuelled by malicious individuals' who posted grievances online.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share  Save  Imane Khelif, the Algerian boxer at the centre of a gender dispute at the Paris Olympic Games, has filed a legal complaint against the social media platform X for harassment.\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9992880564364516, \"rank\": 0.0005410043221623668, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thegold medal winner'slawyer said on Saturday that she filed the formal complaint in France.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9376528925689286, \"rank\": 0.03891579080695782, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif and another gold medallist, Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting, have been at the centre of a high-profile dispute over gender identity that has provoked heated debate on social media.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999515298303455, \"rank\": 3.837824628061692e-05, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Citing court documents, the French newspaper Le Monde reported that the boxing champion \\\"filed a complaint against X\\\" with the Paris correctional court, the national centre for combating online harassment.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.87557298761563, \"rank\": 0.1414021668562258, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Monde\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\"}, {\"begin\": 708, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994898045252, \"rank\": 5.101958235165753e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's lawyer Nabil Boudi said the complaint was filed on Friday.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The boxer Imane Khelif has decided to begin a new fight, a fight for justice, dignity and honour,\\\" he said in a statement as he announced the complaint for \\\"aggravated online harassment \\u2026 [had been filed] to Paris prosecutors\\\".\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994898045252, \"rank\": 5.101958235165753e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All that is being said about me on social media is immoral.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to change the minds of people around the world,\\\" Khelif said.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Individuals in the complaint were described as \\\"important political figures\\\" with wide followings on X, the social media company owned by Tesla and SpaceX CEO Elon Musk.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\", \"score\": 0.9999803397120087, \"rank\": 1.9660674561941493e-05, \"text\": \"Tesla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tesla_Model_3\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpaceX\", \"score\": 0.9999999934425432, \"rank\": 6.557465992240972e-09, \"text\": \"SpaceX\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpaceX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpaceX\"}, {\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The posts targeting Khelif \\\"exceeded 100 million views,\\\" it added.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The speculation was \\\"fuelled by malicious individuals,\\\" Boudi said.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The investigation will determine who was behind this misogynist, racist and sexist campaign but will also have to concern itself with those who fed the online lynching.\\\"\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The furore over Khelif's eligibility drew fire from the likes of former United States President Donald Trump, Harry Potter author JK Rowling and several right-wing French politicians.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_presidential_election\", \"score\": 0.9999998153500826, \"rank\": 1.8464991452121514e-07, \"text\": \"United States President\", \"types\": [\"Q40231\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_presidential_election\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_presidential_election\"}, {\"begin\": 1792, \"end\": 1804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999857384689828, \"rank\": 1.4261694702421072e-05, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1806, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9999999613403369, \"rank\": 3.788834181466915e-08, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 1826, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.87557298761563, \"rank\": 0.1414021668562258, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After her gold medal victory on Friday night, Khelif said winning was the perfect response to \\\"attacks\\\" and \\\"bullying\\\" and declared: \\\"I am a woman like any other.\\\"\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The questions regarding Khelif's and Lin's gender were sparked by the International Boxing Association (IBA).\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5035000911657994e-17, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2156, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.999857821933482, \"rank\": 0.00014219801534392867, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At a news conference last week, the IBA's Kremlin-linked president, Umar Kremlev, claimed the organisation had run \\\"genetic testing that shows that these are men\\\".\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.999857821933482, \"rank\": 0.00014219801534392867, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2231, \"end\": 2235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"score\": 0.9999987218560801, \"rank\": 1.2781439566796706e-06, \"text\": \"Umar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA threw both boxers out of the world championships in 2023.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.999857821933482, \"rank\": 0.00014219801534392867, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee, however, cleared them to box in Paris.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994898045252, \"rank\": 5.101958235165753e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if she would take measures similar to Khelif, Lin said: \\\"This is something I will discuss with my team.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will decide later what the next step will be.\\\"\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following an early round victory for Khelif in the ring, Rowling referred to the boxer as a \\\"male\\\" and accused her of \\\"enjoying the distress of a woman he's just punched in the head, and whose life's ambition he's just shattered\\\".\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump declared in capital letters on his Truth Social outlet: \\\"I will keep men out of women's sports\\\".\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2905, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truth_Social\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Truth Social\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truth_Social\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truth_Social\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His vice-presidential nominee, JD Vance, argued that \\\"Kamala Harris's ideas about gender\\\" have led \\\"to a grown man pummelling a woman in a boxing match\\\".\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"score\": 0.582178686224707, \"rank\": 0.7085969960443156, \"text\": \"JD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Juris_Doctor\"}, {\"begin\": 3001, \"e